 Apocalypse grinned. There could be only noe pred empire. And that empire 
would be controled by drillbit. He walked into the engine room. He looked at 
Killfest. "The time is now. We must destroy megatron while we have the 
chance. I expect destron support against him. There will be only one empire. 
That is this one." He sent a comm to Darkmouse. "Please come to the engine 
room."
